      <p>Slax Reader is provided "as is" without any guarantees or warranties, express or implied. To the extent permitted by law, we will not be liable for any loss or damage arising from your use of Slax Reader.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="terms__section">
      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us via the contact information provided.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="terms__section">
      <h2>Governing Law</h2>
      <p>These terms and conditions are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the jurisdiction where we are based.</p>
    </section>

    <p class="terms__closing">By using Slax Reader, you signify your acceptance of these Terms of Service. Thank you for choosing us!</p>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .terms {
    padding: 64px 0 100px;
    background: #ffffff;
  }

  .terms__inner {
    max-width: 780px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }

  .terms__title {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #1f1f1f;
  }

  .terms__divider {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    margin: 0 0 28px;
  }

  .terms__date {
    margin: 0 0 48px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #888888;
  }

  .terms__section {
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }

  .terms__section h2 {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1f1f1f;
  }

  .terms__section p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #444444;
  }

  .terms__closing {
    margin-top: 48px;
    padding-top: 32px;
    border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: #666666;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
</style>
